ulate SOC dynamics in temperate and subtropical soils. No-till under moderate C/N inputs recovered topsoil SOC, but subsurface losses offset SOC accrual. Use of CA, organic amendments and best practice crop management (BP) is crucial for long-term SOC storage and permanence.},
